description: A blue watered silk tapestry hangs on one of the plain wooden walls, and a modwir beam ceiling rises overhead.  A pile of striped throw pillows sits in one corner of a polished oak floor.  There is a gilded maple table on one side of the shop and an aqua-hued seaglass display on the other.
